{"data":[{"date":"10:38 20/07","title":"L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a HLV Wenger","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/4/lo-ben-do-cuc-soc-cua-hlv-wenger.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Wenger</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi chia tay Arsenal sau h\u01a1n 20 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, HLV Wenger v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi m\u1eddi. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 68 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"R\u1eddi Arsenal, HLV Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"R\u1eddi Arsenal, HLV Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/lo-ben-do-cuc-soc-cua-hlv-wenger.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Wenger v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Theo Daily Mail, Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m nay, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Vahid Halilhodzic (ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia) v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Akira Nishino. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 63 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf hoa Anh \u0111\u00e0o v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f2n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, song c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i 3-2. D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Akira Nishino \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t HLV n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Wenger nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 HLV Wenger l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Wenger t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 m\u00f9a 1995/96 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB Nagoya Grampus Eight c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, sau khi r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u00f4ng m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wenger\" title=\"Wenger\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/15/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-16-chu-tu-wenger-se-thay-the-zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Wenger c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn, Iniesta v\u00e0 Fernando Torres \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc x\u1ee9 s\u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u00f4ng Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110TQG n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1448","checkdouble":"191651"},{"date":"11:06 20/07","title":"Chelsea ch\u1ed1t 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/chelsea-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-courois.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Hi\u1ec7n The Blues \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Courtois s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKeylor Navas v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, song n\u0103m nay anh \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n. Thibaut Courtois \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Chelsea nh\u1eafm n\u1ebfu Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Chelsea nh\u1eafm n\u1ebfu Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/chelsea-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-courois.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thibaut Courtois s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Courtois \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb dao \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu. C\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Madrid, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i TBN \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ed1t ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Hi\u1ec7n The Blues \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma\" title=\"Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Milan-muon-doi-Donnarumma-lay-Morata-cua-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gianluigi Donnarumma \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm thay Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEvening Standard kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh danh s\u00e1ch 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Chelsea bao g\u1ed3m Donnarumma c\u1ee7a AC Milan, Kasper Schmeichel c\u1ee7a\u00a0Leicester City v\u00e0 Petr Cech c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/khong-the-gay-soc-vu-alisson-chelsea-chuyen-huong-sang-donnarumma-172-191596.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Donnarumma</span>, n\u1ebfu AC Milan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Kasper Schmeichel. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Leicester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d gi\u1eef th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1 Chelsea s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i mua l\u1ea1i Petr Cech, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Donnarumma, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00f9ng Alvaro Morata trao \u0111\u1ed5i. The Blues s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan nh\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 19 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1447","checkdouble":"191653"},{"date":"11:28 20/07","title":"\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Mexico. Juan Mata l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap M.U tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</h2><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Mexico. Juan Mata l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap M.U tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</h2>\r\nDanh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Sergio Romero, Joel Pereira, Lee Grant<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7: Antonio Valencia, Matteo Darmian, Diogo Dalot, Timothy  Fosu-Mensah, RoShaun Williams, Chris Smalling, Eric Bailly, Axel  Tuanzebe, Demetri Mitchell, Luke Shaw<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: James Garner, Ander Herrera, Andreas Pereira, Scott McTominay, Ethan Hamilton<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: Tahith Chong, Angel Gomes, Juan Mata, Anthony Martial, Mason Greenwood, Joshua Bohui.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-club-america-tran-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191627.html\">MU 1-1 Club America (KT): Juan Mata c\u1ee9u Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf h\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-don-tin-cuc-vui-ve-alexis-sanchez-172-191630.html\">M.U \u0111\u00f3n tin c\u1ef1c vui v\u1ec1 Alexis Sanchez</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ibra-tiet-lo-nguyen-nhan-buoc-phai-roi-mu-172-191638.html\">Ibra ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1446","checkdouble":"191654"},{"date":"10:49 20/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 20 V-League: \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA \u2013 HAGL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/14/truoc-vong-20-vleague-dai-chien-slna-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 20 V-League 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111ang d\u1ed3n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa SLNA vs HAGL, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><h2>\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA &ndash; HAGL<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00f2ng 20 V-League, CLB HAGL s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c mang t\u00ean SLNA tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a NHM b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi su\u1ed1t 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1eady, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u0169ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 13 cho t\u1edbi nay. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 4 tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 20 V-League \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA &ndash; HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 20 V-League \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA &ndash; HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/14/truoc-tran-hagl-vs-slna-chuyen-gia-mach-nuoc-cho-doi-bong-xu-nghe.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;SLNA vs HAGL l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i&nbsp;v\u00f2ng 20 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda HAGL, h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 &lsquo;y\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng v\u00eda&rsquo; khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u00fang \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y khi &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Thanh H\u00f3a hay b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t SLNA ch\u1ec9 &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1ea1ng&rsquo;, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i trong l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i SLNA v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 g\u1eb7p S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1edbi t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 &ldquo;hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng&rdquo; c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00ec l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang sa s\u00fat sau chu\u1ed7i 10 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 13 tr\u00ean BXH v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t v\u00e0 x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean BXH. Do \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u nay, XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 &ldquo;chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c&rdquo; c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111ang x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m (17 so v\u1edbi 16). V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn b\u1ee9t l\u00ean kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e1y BXH. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n nay, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi m\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 &ldquo;l\u1ea5n&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Can Tho vs Sai Gon\" title=\"C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/nhan-dinh-can-tho-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-207-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Thanh H\u00f3a c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League n\u0103m nay g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i khi l\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd v\u1eabn b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 hai l\u00e0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a t\u1edbi 14 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y l\u00ean ng\u00f4i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 b\u1ecb ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby. Thanh H\u00f3a l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng tuy nhi\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c sau nh\u1eefng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a d\u00e0n sao tr\u1ebb Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Ki\u00ean, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0103n Th\u00e1i Qu\u00fd.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thanh hoa vs Ha Noi\" title=\"thanh h\u00f3a vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/anh1_1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thanh H\u00f3a \u1edf 3 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng, Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i chi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1i sau 5 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, d\u00f9 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong c\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi Thanh H\u00f3a trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 0-3 ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 CLB TP.HCM vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bongda24h s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau vong 20 V-League 2018\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Vong-20-V-League.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-can-tho-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-207-vleague-2018-344-191652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/nhan-dinh-can-tho-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-207-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-can-tho-vs-sai-gon-17h00-ngay-207-vleague-2018-344-191652.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 17h00 ng\u00e0y 20/7 (V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 20/7 (V\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1445","checkdouble":"191655"},{"date":"11:16 20/07","title":"Neymar ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/neymar-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi PSG d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb CLB Real Madrid.</h2><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">Neymar l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">\u00a0<br>\r\n</span>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Neymar l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Neymar-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Neymar t\u00e1i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi CLB PSG trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi chia tay si\u00eau sao Ronaldo, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf CR7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 Neymar l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Los Blancos nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 \u2018ve v\u00e3n\u2019 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Fox Sports trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 l\u00e0m t\u1eeb thi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat PSG cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch cao h\u01a1n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u. D\u01b0 lu\u1eadn th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Real nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u1eafc c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m t\u00f4i d\u00e0nh cho PSG l\u1edbn bi\u1ebft nh\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0o\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1c, t\u1edd AS th\u00e2n CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft HLV m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a PSG l\u00e0 \u00f4ng Tuchel kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1eafm v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Neymar \u1edf World Cup, v\u00e0 \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a PSG xoay quanh sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe.\u00a0V\u00ec th\u1ebf PSG ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb Los Blancos.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Roboto-Regular, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-van-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-neymar-180-191642.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/6/real-madrid-van-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-neymar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-van-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-neymar-180-191642.html\">Real Madrid v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid mua Neymar th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-neymar-da-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-197-191453.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/17/psg-neymar-da-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-neymar-da-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-197-191453.html\">PSG: Neymar \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span><br>\r\nLuis Fernandez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/effenberg-so-sanh-mandzukic-va-neymar-421-191231.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/effenberg-so-sanh-mandzukic-va-neymar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/effenberg-so-sanh-mandzukic-va-neymar-421-191231.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c: T\u00f4i th\u00edch Mandzukic g\u1ea5p 10 Neymar</span><br>\r\nEffenberg so s\u00e1nh Mandzukic v\u00e0 Neymar. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u1eebng danh tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Mario Mandzukic s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 200 tri\u1ec7u Euro.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nThanh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1444","checkdouble":"191656"},{"date":"11:02 20/07","title":"Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 1-1 Club America (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/video-tong-hop-mu-11-club-america-giao-huu-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Mexico. Juan Mata l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap M.U tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</h2><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Mexico. Juan Mata l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap M.U tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</h2>\r\nDanh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Sergio Romero, Joel Pereira, Lee Grant<br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7: Antonio Valencia, Matteo Darmian, Diogo Dalot, Timothy  Fosu-Mensah, RoShaun Williams, Chris Smalling, Eric Bailly, Axel  Tuanzebe, Demetri Mitchell, Luke Shaw<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: James Garner, Ander Herrera, Andreas Pereira, Scott McTominay, Ethan Hamilton<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: Tahith Chong, Angel Gomes, Juan Mata, Anthony Martial, Mason Greenwood, Joshua Bohui.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-club-america-tran-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191627.html\">MU 1-1 Club America (KT): Juan Mata c\u1ee9u Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf h\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-don-tin-cuc-vui-ve-alexis-sanchez-172-191630.html\">M.U \u0111\u00f3n tin c\u1ef1c vui v\u1ec1 Alexis Sanchez</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ibra-tiet-lo-nguyen-nhan-buoc-phai-roi-mu-172-191638.html\">Ibra ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1443","checkdouble":"191657"},{"date":"11:19 20/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 20/7: M.U c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t Pogba v\u00e0o tay Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/ngay-hom-nay-207.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (20/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n<h2>M.U c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t Pogba v\u00e0o tay Barca\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/mourinho-pogba-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\nT\u1edd Mundo loan b\u00e1o, Paul Pogba s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi MU, h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca. T\u00e2n gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan, Ramon Planes, m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Gatafe c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 th\u00e1ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPlanes ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t th\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba - c\u00f2 b\u1ef1 Mino Raiola. Ngu\u1ed3n tin cho hay, tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mino Raiol \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf l\u00f2 La Masia \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Paul Pogba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Pogba v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018, v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y n\u00f3 c\u00e0ng n\u00f3ng l\u00ean b\u1edfi anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean m\u1ed9t \"t\u1ea7m m\u1edbi\" th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua.\r\n<h2>Navas n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Real, d\u1ecdn ch\u1ed7 cho Courtois</h2>\r\nTr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Keylor Navas v\u1eeba b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chia s\u1ebb th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u1ea9n \u00fd. Navas \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i \u0111o\u1ea1n video ghi l\u1ea1i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n anh n\u00e2ng c\u00fap c\u00f9ng Real. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p chia tay m\u00e0 Navas g\u1eedi t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 31 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ra \u0111i trong H\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn ch\u1ed7 cho Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Bernabeu.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 207, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 207, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-207,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Keylor Navas</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ef7 ph\u00fa Abramovich \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n sang Italia ch\u1ed1t 2 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d</h2>\r\nTheo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u00ean t\u1eeb Corriere dello Sport (Italia), t\u1ef7 ph\u00fa Roman Abramovich do kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1p chuy\u1ebfn bay t\u1edbi Italia g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 nh\u00e0 m\u00f4i gi\u1edbi Fali Ramadani, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea thu\u00ea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Gonzalo Higuain \u2013 Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Nh\u01b0ng theo ngu\u1ed3n tin n\u00e0y cho hay, gi\u1eefa 2 b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 100 tri\u1ec7u euro (89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) cho 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Higuain v\u00e0 Rugani.\r\n<h2>Thiago Alcantara mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Barcelona</h2>\r\nTheo t\u1edd AS, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Thiago Alcantara \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Barcelona. CLB x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Iniesta. Bayern Munich s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u01a1n l\u00fd.\r\n<h2>Rabiot t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG</h2>\r\nT\u1edd Mundo Deportivo cho hay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rabiot \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00f2ng v\u1edbi PSG. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p lo l\u1eafng b\u1edfi trong th\u1eddi gian qua, Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<h2>Alisson ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Liverpool</h2>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker t\u1eeb AS Roma theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 cho Roma 62,5 tri\u1ec7u euro (56 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t. C\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi 10 tri\u1ec7u euro ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed, t\u1ed5ng chi ph\u00ed cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 72,5 tri\u1ec7u euro (65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Brazil \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Liverpool. Chia s\u1ebb trong ng\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp CLB m\u1edbi, Alisson cho bi\u1ebft anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn Anfield sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin nh\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah. Alisson tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a The Kop trong H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, sau Naby Keita, Fabinho, Xherdan Shaqiri.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/Premier-League-chiem-nua-doi-hinh-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Liverpool k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson</span><br>\r\n<span>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1442","checkdouble":"191658"},{"date":"11:29 20/07","title":"Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson: H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 De Gea c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/liverpool-chieu-mo-alisson-ho-da-co-de-gea-cua-rieng-minh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 g\u1ea7n 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng The Kop \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t David De Gea xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1eefa tr\u1ecb &ldquo;g\u00f3t Achilles&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft C\u0110V Liverpool mong \u0111\u1ee3i r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi. C\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp s\u00e2n Anfield t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e8 nh\u01b0 Naby Keita, Fabinho hay Xherdan Shaqiri c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd b\u1eb1ng Alisson Becker. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c</span> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB n\u00e0y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng Keita, Fabinho hay Shaqiri gi\u00fap Liverpool c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng <em>Alisson th\u00ec gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f2n t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i</em>. N\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Kop nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, C\u0110V c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd h\u00e9t l\u00ean hai ch\u1eef &ldquo;Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 De Gea c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 De Gea c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/Liverpool-chieu-mo-Alisson-Ho-da-co-De-Gea-cua-rieng-minh!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Karius v\u00e0 Mignolet kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin \u1edf Klopp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Alisson gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ed1c n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ecdc tinh khi\u1ebft d\u00e0nh cho Liverpool</strong> sau nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng d\u00e0i d\u1eb1ng d\u1eb7c ch\u1ec9 u\u1ed1ng c\u00e0 ph\u00ea hay tr\u00e0. M\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e0 ph\u00ea hay tr\u00e0 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9c u\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u01b0a th\u00edch, song n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ecdc m\u1edbi l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 gi\u00fap cho m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n3 n\u0103m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jurgen Klopp, Liverpool lu\u00f4n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0m say \u0111\u1eafm l\u00f2ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, <u>danh hi\u1ec7u l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 lu\u00f4n l\u1ea9n tr\u00e1nh h\u1ecd</u>. \u0110\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft t\u1eeb c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n, Europa League t\u1edbi Champions League song The Kop lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp chi trich Karius\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Karius\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/thua-tham-real-klopp-bat-luc-voi-sai-lam-cua-toi-do-karius.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u1ea3ng tr\u00e1nh Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Premier League, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng giai \u0111o\u1ea1n h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay song v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t th\u1eddi Klopp t\u1edbi nay v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 4. L\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea3o nhau &ldquo;H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 cho m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u&rdquo;. Theo c\u00e1ch ngh\u0129 n\u00e0y, Liverpool ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c xu h\u01b0\u1edbng. H\u1ecd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t d\u1eef d\u1ed9i song l\u1ea1i mong manh n\u01a1i h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi khu v\u1ef1c trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Virgil van Dijk, gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac <u>Liverpool ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb &ldquo;g\u00f3t Achilles&rdquo; c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</u>. Nh\u1eefng Simon Mignolet hay Loris Karius \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Klopp trao r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i song \u0111\u1ec1u phung ph\u00ed. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n ng\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, ngay tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft Champions League, m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi v\u1edbi Karius v\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Liverpool. Nh\u00ecn t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, Liverpool thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid b\u1edfi 2 sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n h\u01a1n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n Karius.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u1edbi Karius</span><br>\r\n<span>C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trang th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Opta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nT\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c De Gea c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c David De Gea</em> c\u1ee7a Man United. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ebfn De Gea trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1edbi M.U c\u00f2n m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 sai s\u00f3t. Nh\u01b0ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t, nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ban \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng g\u1ee3i m\u1edf v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\" target=\"_blank\">L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Alisson</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e2m l\u00fd. V\u1edbi c\u00fa s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid, ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft bao gi\u1edd Karius m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. \u1ede tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 4 Anh Tranmere Rovers m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 pha b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua. N\u00f3 x\u00f3a tan m\u1ecdi b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c m\u00e0 Klopp d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng sau chung k\u1ebft Champions League t\u1edbi nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea va Alisson\" title=\"De Gea va Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/De-Gea-va-Alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c De Gea c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson trong tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i s\u01b0\u1edbng r\u01a1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 C\u0110V m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 thay v\u00ec n\u01a1m n\u1edbp lo s\u1ee3 khi \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mignolet hay Karius.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKarius c\u00f3 dung m\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb th\u1ea7n Hy L\u1ea1p v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao 1m89 c\u00f9ng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t g\u00f3c c\u1ea1nh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch anh xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng c\u00f4 g\u00e1i xem ra ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0&hellip; \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Alisson. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t De Gea c\u1ee7a Liverpool, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed5ng l\u1ef1c m\u00e0 Klopp x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng t\u1ea1i Liverpool c\u00f3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn t\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 y\u00ean v\u1ecb trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Alisson\" title=\"thu mon Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-146-MU-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-tu-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Alisson r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i cho Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf, chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Liverpool tr\u1edf n\u00ean qu\u00e1 r\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi Karius v\u00e0 Mignolet. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, <strong>Alisson l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng gian t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n cho The Kop</strong>. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t gi\u00fap tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian x\u1eed l\u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlisson c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Ederson, lu\u00f4n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 Alisson c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i (67 so v\u1edbi 36) v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0110T Brazil thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span><br>\r\n<span>Sau nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 25 tu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng hay c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00f2n hay h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Ederson, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 trong danh s\u00e1ch gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t Premier League 2017/18, ch\u1ec9 sau De Gea. N\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Liverpool nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, Alisson sinh ra l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do Klopp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. C\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a anh, Liverpool th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson: Khi &ldquo;bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t&rdquo; t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emre-can-cam-on-va-tam-biet-nhung-liverpool-se-chang-nho-anh-dau-172-187346.html\">Emre Can: C\u1ea3m \u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t, nh\u01b0ng Liverpool s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1edb anh \u0111\u00e2u!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-sang-liverpool-them-mot-lan-cai-tat-vao-mu-172-187307.html\">Fabinho sang Liverpool: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n c\u00e1i t\u00e1t v\u00e0o MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-xay-ra-sau-khi-liverpool-cuop-mat-fabinho-tu-mu-172-187275.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra sau khi Liverpool c\u01b0\u1edbp m\u1ea5t Fabinho t\u1eeb MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tham-hoa-loris-karius-kiem-cui-9-thang-thieu-90-phut-184-187196.html\">Th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda Loris Karius: Ki\u1ebfm c\u1ee7i 9 th\u00e1ng, thi\u00eau 90 ph\u00fat...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1441","checkdouble":"191659"},{"date":"11:35 20/07","title":"Alisson Becker: Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh Liverpool \u2013 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/alisson-becker-giai-ma-tan-binh-liverpool-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker t\u1eeb AS Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, bi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao Brazil tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng Hai \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u trong khung th\u00e0nh s\u00e2n Anfield, Jurgen Klopp b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi: \u201cGi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3, t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 trong tay. C\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.\u201d</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mua Alisson Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mua Alisson Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/Liverpool-mua-Alisson-Giai-ma-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Loris Karius kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i qu\u00e1 t\u1ed3i, nh\u01b0ng anh l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \"ng\u00e1o\" ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fd mu\u00f4n thu\u1edf, anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee9 mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ea5y. Th\u1ebf l\u00e0 tr\u00f4i \u0111i n\u0103m th\u00e1ng, sau m\u1ed9t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/tham-hoa-loris-karius-kiem-cui-9-thang-thieu-90-phut-184-187196.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Loris Karius</span> v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil, Liverpool ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec Alisson Becker, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb AS Roma.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ed3i d\u00e0o t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh sau nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tham d\u1ef1 Champions League, c\u1ed9ng h\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u00e2n qu\u1ef9 d\u01b0 d\u1ea3 nh\u1edd th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 b\u00e1n Philippe Coutinho cho Barcelona, Liverpool ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd t\u1ef1 tin \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m v\u1eeba qua, ngu\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00f4 bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u1eb1m \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng pressing, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tam t\u1ea5u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t hai c\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Sadio Mane. Tuy nhi\u00ean gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf\u00a0 v\u00f9ng Merseyside s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5c d\u1ecdc x\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9ng c\u00e1p v\u00e0 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc, v\u1edbi Virgil Van Dijk, Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Alisson.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/Premier-League-chiem-nua-doi-hinh-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Liverpool k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Alisson<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, Alisson h\u1eb5n c\u00f2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00ean g\u00e2y h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa, k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V Liverpool h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u00e2u lo, \u00e1i ng\u1ea1i. 26 tu\u1ed5i, Alisson c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n \u1edf Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t CLB, v\u1eady m\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i s\u1edbm l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a ngay c\u1ea3 si\u00eau \u0111\u1ea1i gia Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu anh t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u duy tr\u00ec ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady cho c\u1ea3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00e2y, bi\u1ebfn 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh con s\u1ed1 nh\u1ecf b\u00e9, r\u1ebb b\u00e8o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson Becker Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh Liverpool \u2013 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Alisson Becker Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh Liverpool \u2013 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Alisson-Becker-Giai-ma-tan-binh-Liverpool-\u2013-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Alisson \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho Brazil \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, sinh tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf bang Rio Grande do Sul v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1edfi CLB Internacional. M\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 83 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee9ng khung g\u1ed7 khi gia nh\u1eadp Roma n\u0103m 2016, Alisson ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Wojciech Szczesny c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Serie A. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn khi c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, c\u1edd m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn tay Alisson v\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u1ea5t n\u00f3, v\u1edbi 49 tr\u1eadn b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 ba Serie A c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u00ecu m\u1ebfn \u0111\u1eb7t bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cgoleiro gato\u201d, d\u1ecbch ra ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \u201cch\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb9p trai\u201d, v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng Alisson kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ngh\u1ec1 tay tr\u00e1i ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam thu nh\u1eadp, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u01a1n th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u00e0 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<table cellpacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"44px\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"/content/images/s1.png\" alt=\"comment left\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Alisson \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n th\u1ebf nhi\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi Alisson nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t Messi trong khung th\u00e0nh, ai \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng v\u1ec1 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Dino Zoff.</em></div>\r\n            <span style=\"color: #8bc53f; float: right;\"><em>Roberto Negrisolo, c\u1ef1u HLV th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Roma.</em></span></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"44px\"><img src=\"/content/images/s2.png\" alt=\"comment right\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson gia nhap Liverpool\" title=\"Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Premier-League-chiem-nua-doi-hinh-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Alisson v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd do Liverpool ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t v\u00ec Alisson<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi nghi\u1ec5m nhi\u00ean t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed7i khi c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh: Li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng anh ta c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed hay kh\u00f4ng? Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Liverpool mua Alisson, c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi d\u00f5ng d\u1ea1c \u2013 C\u00f3, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng cho Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf Anfield kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i, v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng \u00edt m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n trong khung g\u1ed7, nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu t\u00ednh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ebft ch\u00f3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"nhung con so so sanh Alisson voi Karius\" title=\"nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Alisson, t\u00e2n binh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda Karius</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u b\u1eb1ng hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 l\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 n\u00f3i chung c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. Quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, Alisson s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c th\u00edch nghi, h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool khi Roma c\u1ee7a anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c C\u0110V Liverpool s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00e0ng th\u00eam ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Alisson ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. Kh\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u1edbt nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng, nh\u01b0 David De Gea c\u1ee7a Manchester United, nh\u01b0ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u cho m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p Champions League ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e2y, trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh h\u01a1n 20 tr\u1eadn \u1edf n\u0103m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Alisson ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu x\u1ebfp sau De Gea v\u00e0 Jan Oblak c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea va Alisson\" title=\"De Gea va Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/De-Gea-va-Alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Alisson kh\u00f4ng thua g\u00ec De Gea c\u1ee7a Man Utd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span class=\"mfirst-letter\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#333333\">\u0110\u1ea5y l\u00e0 Roma ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1n gi\u00e1 cao b\u1eb1ng Man Utd hay Atletico v\u00e0 k\u1ec3 ra m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u00f3i l\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u, khi n\u00f3 c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o ki\u1ec3u d\u1ea1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span class=\"mfirst-letter\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#333333\">V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Atletico Madrid b\u1eadc th\u1ea7y ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3i s\u00fat xa c\u1ea7u may t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba h\u00f2ng gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, Oblak hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u1ee9u thua nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, phong c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ngh\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Atletico. \u0110\u00f3 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng pressing t\u1eeb xa thay v\u00ec co c\u1ee5m khu v\u1ef1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ea9y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jurgen Klopp v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf hi\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb1ng sau ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1edbi s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u1ea3i nguy trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng 1v1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u1edbi Karius</span><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trang th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Opta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Alisson x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi hay kh\u00f4ng?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng Ederson hay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng ph\u00e2n n\u1eeda trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u00e0y nay (kho\u1ea3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), v\u1eady n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf cho r\u1eb1ng Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 mua \u0111\u1eaft Alisson. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 b\u1eb5ng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Courtois ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, trong khi ch\u00ednh Alisson khi\u1ebfn Ederson, ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 vua n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh Man City, ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ph\u1eadn d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Brazil.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Alisson ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng. Liverpool c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0m v\u1eady nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean. Kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed soi m\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Alisson.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson cua Liverpool\" title=\"Alisson cua Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Alisson-cua-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Alisson v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i n\u00e0y th\u00ec m\u1ea5t c\u00e1i kia, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n c\u00e2n so s\u00e1nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan gi\u1eefa kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba v\u00e0 \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t 1v1. \u0110\u01a1n c\u1eed, nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n cao r\u00e1o nh\u01b0 Courtois hay Petr Cech c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng n\u00f3i chung, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u00e2ng cao nh\u01b0 Hugo Lloris hay Marc-Andre ter Stegen.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Alisson th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kho\u1ea3n ch\u1ed1ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ed1n d\u0129 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u kinh ni\u00ean c\u1ee7a Liverpool, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u01a1i m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Liverpool mua Alisson v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool-172-191633.html\">Alisson n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\">V\u1edbi Alisson, Premier League chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1440","checkdouble":"191660"},{"date":"11:37 20/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 20/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/20/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2007.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 20/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2007-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Eden Hazard v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 125 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo Don Balon, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard, the \u0111\u00f3 Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 125 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gareth Bale s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Bernabeu ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c n\u1ebfu...</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Marca, Gareth Bale s\u1ebd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Bernabeu n\u1ebfu Real mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Hi\u1ec7n K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Mbappe, Neymar v\u00e0 Hazard \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n mang Marcelo t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcelo c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. \u0110\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mua Mauro Icardi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2007 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/22/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2007-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mauro Icardi gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Inter Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Inter Milan, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho tham v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Thibaut Courtois</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Thibaut Courtois v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, vi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic-180-191234.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic </span>n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, hi\u1ec7n Man City, MU v\u00e0 Tottenham l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lucas Vazquez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vazquez gap kho o tran Real vs Bayern\" title=\"Vazquez gap kho o tran Real vs Bayern\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/2/Benzema-tran-Real-vs-Bayern-Chu-chim-trong-truyen-thuyet-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Vazquez\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lucas Vazquez, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Los Blancos b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Anthony Martial b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford, song Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1439","checkdouble":"191661"},{"date":"07:11 20/07","title":"Fabinho: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 r\u1ee7 r\u00ea Mbappe t\u1edbi Liverpool\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/fabinho-toi-dang-co-ru-re-mbappe-toi-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Monaco, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabinho thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Mbappe t\u1edbi Liverpool \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nFabinho c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o Mbappe<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m nay, Fabinho l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Kylian Mbappe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y s\u1ed1t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ghi 4 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Khi t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Kylian \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t tin nh\u1eafn ch\u00fac m\u1eebng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00ec tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m c\u00f9ng \u0110T th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, Kylian l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng l\u1edbn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i PSG. Kh\u00f4ng sao c\u1ea3, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool. T\u00f4i c\u00f9ng r\u1ea5t th\u00e2n v\u1edbi Bernardo Silva c\u00f9ng Benjamin Mendy. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng t\u1edbi Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabinho thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Mbappe t\u1edbi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fabinho thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Mbappe t\u1edbi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Fabinho-thuyet-phuc-Mbappe-toi-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fabinho thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Mbappe sang Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nFabinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: &ldquo;Khi t\u1edbi Real Madrid, t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 18, 19 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng si\u00eau sao l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Cris Ronaldo, Mesut Ozil, Luka Modric. Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Real Madrid B gi\u00fap t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Liverpool &ndash; m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\" bong da\" type=\" bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Liverpool c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u Man City \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, nh\u01b0ng Liverpool s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 ngai v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac&rdquo; &ndash; Fabinho k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh khi \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 Alisson Becker. Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ea5y, trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Fabinho thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Mbappe t\u1edbi Liverpool s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\">V\u1edbi Alisson, Premier League chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1438","checkdouble":"191637"},{"date":"07:34 20/07","title":"Ibra ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/ibra-tiet-lo-nguyen-nhan-buoc-phai-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi y\u00ean \u1ed5n t\u1ea1i MLS, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Zlatan Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nIbra bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u CLB trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean &ndash; 27 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 45 tr\u1eadn, Ibra \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Rooney v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 2, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ghi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 36 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n x\u1ecf gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n nong, h\u00e3y gi\u1eef l\u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng tinh th\u1ea7n d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, M.U \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Zlatan. C\u00f2n t\u00f4i v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Zlatan. T\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng v\u1edbi Mourinho: &lsquo;Nghe n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, h\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn ai \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&rsquo;.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU va nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU va nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/ibra.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Ibra c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169: &ldquo;Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 b\u1eb1ng l\u1eddi. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Pogba c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Rooney, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span></span> theo m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i MLS. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Rooney, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 n\u00f3 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. Rooney n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y&rdquo; &ndash; Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien-465-190650.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien-465-190650.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn, Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll v\u00ec l\u1ee1 d\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham</span><br>\r\nSau khi \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Zlatan Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll b\u1edfi Rooney c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1edbi David Beckham.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-469-191326.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-469-191326.html\">Ibrahimovic khen Pogba sau danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nZlatan Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho Pogba sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u00eam qua.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1437","checkdouble":"191638"},{"date":"07:48 20/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u1edbi Karius","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trang th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Opta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAlisson \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda Karius<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Alisson Becker. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng xem th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 g\u00ec h\u01a1n Loris Karius qua nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>28 &ndash;</strong> Alisson l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 28 b\u00e0n thua trong 37 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Serie A m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u00edt h\u01a1n 10 b\u00e0n so v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Mignolet (24) v\u00e0 Karius (14) t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>109 &ndash;</strong> Alisson c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 109 pha c\u1ee9u thua \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Mignolet (36) v\u00e0 Karius (31).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>79,3 &ndash; </strong>T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Alisson Becker. Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Mignolet/Karius l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 59,3 v\u00e0 68,9%.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/karius.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n0 &ndash;</strong> Alisson kh\u00f4ng m\u1eafc b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 sai l\u1ea7m n\u00e0o d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua, trong khi Mignolet c\u00f3 3 v\u00e0 Karius c\u00f3 2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>118,9 &ndash;</strong> Kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian trung b\u00ecnh Alisson l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi, kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Karius (122 ph\u00fat/b\u00e0n thua). Tuy nhi\u00ean, Karius b\u1eaft \u00edt h\u01a1n Alisson t\u1edbi 18 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>47 &ndash;</strong> S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Alisson m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trong khi Mignolet v\u00e0 Karius nh\u1eadn t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 61 b\u00e0n thua sau 55 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>8,31 </strong>&ndash; S\u1ed1 trung b\u00ecnh Alisson t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i &lsquo;b\u00e0n th\u1eafng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng&rsquo; (n\u00f3i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 anh c\u1ee9u thua trung b\u00ecnh 8,31 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t), ch\u1ec9 sau Nick Pope (10,26) v\u00e0 David De Gea (13,66) tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. \u0110\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh, con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Karius l\u00e0 -0,64, c\u00f2n Mignolet l\u00e0 -0,81 (ngh\u0129a l\u00e0&hellip; th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\">V\u1edbi Alisson, Premier League chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Liverpool k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1436","checkdouble":"191639"},{"date":"08:05 20/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/7: Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-207-real-madrid-chinh-thuc-dat-gia-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 20/7.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nReal Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Real s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Hazard. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ban \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00e0 Los Blancos chi tr\u1ea3 l\u00e0 125 tri\u1ec7u euro, v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn The Blues s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Thibaut Courtois sau khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/7\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 207 Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-207-Real-Madrid-chinh-thuc-dat-gia-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 20/7: Real mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 Sterling<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Man City. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad s\u1ebd chia tay Sterling trong v\u00f2ng 12 th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>&ldquo;Gi\u00e1o s\u01b0&rdquo; nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Nh\u1eadt<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, L\u0110B\u0110 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eddi HLV Arsene Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0110T B\u1ec9, nh\u01b0ng g\u00e2y ti\u1ebfng vang l\u1edbn khi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Juve<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-sap-cong-bo-tan-binh-thu-2-tri-gia-36-trieu-bang-172-191548.html\" target=\"_blank\">Daniele Rugani s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp The Blues</span> trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t, sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 44,2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (bao g\u1ed3m ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed) c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 77 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7, B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t Diego Godin &ndash; trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3n tin vui tr\u00ean TTCN<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-leicester-sap-co-danny-ward-172-191617.html\" target=\"_blank\">Leicester \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi ra 12,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Danny Ward</span> &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Kasper Schmeichel, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea theo s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Courtois.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">The Kop \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson Becker t\u1eeb AS Roma</span>, sau khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi tr\u1ea3 56 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f9ng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed, khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 207 Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 207 Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-207-Real-Madrid-chinh-thuc-dat-gia-Hazard-hinh-anh-2.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> s\u00e1ng 20/7: Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>M.U nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb Sanchez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9, cho ph\u00e9p anh t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho lo ng\u1ea1i Alexis Sanchez kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00ec r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i visa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1435","checkdouble":"191640"},{"date":"08:54 20/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/20/doi-truong-phap-tiet-lo-dieu-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-truoc-argentina.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Hugo Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng C, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mong ch\u1edd nh\u1ea5t. NHM \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hugo Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hugo Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/doi-truong-phap-tiet-lo-dieu-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-truoc-argentina.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina 4-3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Argentina, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u0103ng hoa. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, Les Bleus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-3.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Argentina ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i. V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 4 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lloris \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hugo Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu thanh Hugo Lloris tranh thu khoe huy chuong cua nha vo dich.\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Hugo Lloris tranh th\u1ee7 khoe huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/4E4F3BC500000578-5958631-image-a-142_1531743694542.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Hugo Lloris tin r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina c\u1ee7a Messi \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00e1p c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u1edf World Cup 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbappe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. Lloris v\u1edbi sai l\u1ea7m trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t danh hi\u1ec7u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o tay Courtois c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1434","checkdouble":"191641"}]}